{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-008__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-008", "source_id": "daya-dang-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·008.1", "text_original": "王命召虎，來旬來宣。文武受命，召公維翰。\n無曰予小子，召公是似。肇敏戎公，用錫爾祉。", "text_normalized": "王命召虎，來旬來宣。文武受命，召公維翰。\n無曰予小子，召公是似。肇敏戎公，用錫爾祉。", "notes": "江漢 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-008__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-008", "source_id": "daya-dang-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·008.2", "text_original": "釐爾圭瓚，秬鬯一卣，告于文人。\n錫山土田，于周受命，自召祖命。\n虎拜稽首，天子萬年。", "text_normalized": "釐爾圭瓚，秬鬯一卣，告于文人。\n錫山土田，于周受命，自召祖命。\n虎拜稽首，天子萬年。", "notes": "江漢 Chinese stanza 2."}
